67640178-561c-423b-9176-e1d2ea8bb1cb.description:
Similar to the blueberry container, but is a separate models + of course the textures.

Interestingly, there are 2 sets of textures for this, 1 titled decor and 1 titled container. the NOR and ASG are the same, but for the dif the decor is 2x the size of the containers one (1024x vs 512x). 
Can be found in the game files since prerelease 0.4 until today (0.6.2).
